  • Get ready to spread a little happiness with every wear!

    Bring the irresistible charm of cute cats into your wardrobe with our soft hoodie featuring a bunch of playful kittens. Throw this hoodie on and style it with your favorite bottoms and fresh kicks. The perfect hoodie for a stroll in the park, hanging out with your friends, and even just at home!

    For that trendy oversized hoodie style, we suggest going up 1+ sizes. Embrace the cuteness overload and cosy up in this fun hoodie. 

    This kawaii hoodie is available in 14 colors and 5 different sizes in 5 different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below.     It is best to measure your chest and length, and then choose a size according to the result to simplify the various international measurements.

    Features

    😍 Promotes warmth, comfort, and durability

    If you are interested in more items like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com.

  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse the garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning
